<item><emphasis effect="italics">P</emphasis>(<emphasis effect="italics">B</emphasis>|<emphasis effect="italics">R</emphasis>) here means <emphasis effect="italics">P</emphasis>(<emphasis effect="italics">B</emphasis> on 2nd|<emphasis effect="italics">R</emphasis> on 1st)</item>
<item><emphasis effect="italics">P</emphasis>(<emphasis effect="italics">R</emphasis>|<emphasis effect="italics">B</emphasis>) here means <emphasis effect="italics">P</emphasis>(<emphasis effect="italics">R</emphasis> on 2nd|<emphasis effect="italics">B</emphasis> on 1st)</item>
