<problem id="eip-idm45711968">
  <para id="element-261">Approximately 86.5 percent of Americans commute to work by car, truck, or van. Out of that group, 84.6 percent drive alone and 15.4 percent drive in a carpool. Approximately 3.9 percent walk to work and approximately 5.3 percent take public transportation.</para>
