    <term>tree diagram</term>
    <meaning id="id18749941">the useful visual representation of a sample space and events in the form of a <emphasis effect="italics">tree</emphasis> with branches marked by possible outcomes together with associated probabilities (frequencies, relative frequencies)</meaning>
